---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Accessibility Statement - Get Global Yields"
  description="Accessibility Statement for Get Global Yields."
>
  <div class="bg-primary-900 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg prose-a:text-accent-500 hover:prose-a:text-accent-400 max-w-none">
        <h1>Accessibility Statement</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-8">Last Updated: July 2026</p>

        <p>Get Global Yields is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for all users, including individuals with disabilities. We continuously work to improve the user experience and apply relevant accessibility standards.</p>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">Accessibility Features</h2>
        <p>Our website includes an accessibility widget (located at the bottom-left corner) that provides the following adjustments:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Text Size:</strong> Increase, decrease, or reset font size</li>
          <li><strong>Contrast:</strong> High contrast mode for improved readability</li>
          <li><strong>Colors:</strong> Grayscale mode</li>
          <li><strong>Links:</strong> Highlight links for easier navigation</li>
          <li><strong>Readable Font:</strong> Switch to a more readable font</li>
          <li><strong>Animations:</strong> Stop animations to reduce motion</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Your settings are saved locally and will persist across visits.</p>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">Conformance Status</h2>
        <p>We aim to conform to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 Level AA. These guidelines define requirements for making web content more accessible to people with disabilities.</p>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">Compliance</h2>
        <p>This accessibility statement is provided in accordance with applicable accessibility regulations, including the Israeli Equal Rights for Persons with Disabilities Law (1998).</p>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you encounter any accessibility barriers or have suggestions for improvement, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
